description: First & First. Stunning 4 story townhome with roof deck, expansive city views, and 2 garage parking! European inspired chef's kitchen designed by Aster Cucine, equipped with Stainless Bosch appliances, wine fridge, quartz counters, and custom cabinetry. Open concept kitchen / living room with oak hardwoods, over-sized floor to ceiling windows, gas fireplace with natural stone surround, and office nook. 3rd floor offers two good-sized bedrooms, custom built in Murphy bed and marble bathroom with double sinks and sliding pocket door for extra privacy. Top floor primary suite fits a king size bed with en-suite bathroom and sliders to private deck. The deck has direct gas line for a Grill and water for plants. Other features include NEST thermostats & surround sound. Ideal location just steps to Seaport, Broadway, Red Line (T), and downtown Boston.
